egin\": 198, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"score\": 0.997631744081328, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarkodie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"lyrics\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"the song\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"Jennifer Lomotey\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"a folklore aboutKrobo women\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"promiscuity\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also referenced his recent conflict with actress Yvonne Nelson, who alleged in her memoir that Sarkodie forced her to abort a pregnancy.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_Jeffries\", \"score\": 0.9906959550549364, \"rank\": 0.008333693658723471, \"text\": \"Yvonne\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_Jeffries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_Jeffries\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"score\": 0.997631744081328, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarkodie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his recent conflict\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"her memoir\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"a pregnancy\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group argued that honouring Sarkodie with a performance platform is concerning, especially for pregnant women, due to his past actions and statements.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"score\": 0.997631744081328, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarkodie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance platform\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnant women\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"his past actions\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"statements\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a letter dated 19 July 2024, Ambassador Jules-Armand Aniambossou clarified that Sarkodie, known privately as Michael Owusu Addo, will not be performing at the openingceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"score\": 0.997631744081328, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarkodie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\"}, {\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999890792425, \"rank\": 1.0920301039031602e-08, \"text\": \"Addo\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"Ambassador Jules-Armand Aniambossou\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the openingceremony\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the embassy stated that his performance is scheduled for the Africa Fan Zone 'Station Afrique' on 9 August 2024,an independent cultural event coinciding with the Olympics.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the embassy\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Africa Fan Zone 'Station Afrique\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"9 August 2024,an\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"independent cultural event\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would like to use this opportunity to clarify that Sarkodie (known in private life as Michael OWUSU ADDO) will not be performing at the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"score\": 0.997631744081328, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarkodie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarkodie_(rapper)\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999890792425, \"rank\": 1.0920301039031602e-08, \"text\": \"ADDO\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addo_Elephant_National_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"private life\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance is scheduled to be part of the Africa Fan Zone 'Station Afrique' which will be held on 9 August 2024 at Stade Robert C\\u00e9sar-L'\\u00cele-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His performance\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the Africa Fan Zone 'Station Afrique\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"9 August\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"Stade Robert C\\u00e9sar-L'\\u00cele-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Station Afrique' is an independent cultural event running concurrently with the Olympic games,\\\"the letter read.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9854425303939309, \"rank\": 0.01476937348672042, \"text\": \"Olympic games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'Station Afrique\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent cultural event\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Embassy acknowledged the concerns raised and cited its commitment to promoting equal human rights, gender equality, and women's empowerment, stating that it does notendorse any form of discrimination.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_mission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.712518272030381e-19, \"text\": \"Embassy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_mission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_mission\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the concerns\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"its commitment\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngra